v1.1.4          19-Nov-2025 - Andrew Leary

                1.  Added the option to suppress adding a tearline in NetMail 
                    areas.

                2.  Added the option for the BBS to add only an empty tearline.

                3.  Reformatted the screen in MBSETUP 1.5 to make room for the
                    new options.

v1.1.3		17-Aug-2025 - Andrew Leary

		1.  Changed the user home directory macro for doors from /U to
                    /H.  /U will now be replaced by the user's Unixname only,
                    to facilitate connecting MBSE to DoorParty or similar
                    services.

v1.1.2		30-Jun-2025 - Andrew Leary

		1.  Updated the German language files to correct an issue with
		    the menu/navigation bar in the message reader.  Thanks to
                    Niels Haedecke for the report and fix.

		2.  Moved the ChangeLog_2024 into the docs/changelogs directory
                    with the rest of the historical ChangeLogs.

v1.1.1		27-Mar-2025 - Andrew Leary

		1.  Updates to the HTML documentation.

		2.  Fixed build errors related to the updated documentation.

		3.  Update copyright notices to 2025.
